ide.backend.variables

Class Variable

  • java.lang.Object
    • ide.backend.variables.Variable
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BooleanVariable, EventInstance, NumberVariable, StringVariable, ValueVariable

    public abstract class Variable
extends java.lang.Object
    The basic variable class. This class is the base class for all different variables used in the IDE Each variable is expressed using an enum.
    Author:
    Axel
